ed colony ships. It rotates to create gravity (strongest at the rim, zero at the hub). \'NASA-punk\' aesthetic: exposed wires, magnetic boots, duct tape, cramped corridors.\",\"\\u2022 ATMOSPHERE: Claustrophobic, cold, industrial. The sound of air scrubbers is constant; silence implies death. The view is the blue Earth below and the infinite black above.\",\"\\u2022 ECONOMY: Air is money. \'Oxygen Credits\' are deducted from wrist implants with every breath. Poverty means suffocation (\'The Walk\').\",\"\\u2022 KEY LOCATIONS: \'Skyforge Docks\' (Zero-G industrial cathedral), \'The Algae Cathedral\' (Glowing green tanks tended by singing priests), \'Deck 4 Command\' (The Admiral connected to the station mind), \'Industrial Ring\' (Sweat and sparks).\",\"\\u2022 TECH & INHABITANTS: \'Void-Born\' (tall, thin, fragile humans adapted to low-g). \'Cyborgs\' (heavily modified dockworkers). Synthetic intelligences managing life support.\",\"--- SPECTRE VISUALS (ANIMA) ---\",\"\\u2022 Magnetica (EM Fields): Blue auroras, floating metal tools, ozone smell, magnetic locking clamps.\",\"\\u2022 Energia (Electricity): Jagged fractals, static discharge, white-hot arcs, battery hum.\",\"\\u2022 Resonantia (Vibration): Visible sound waves, humming metal, vibration-based communication in vacuum.\",\"\\u2022 Spatia (Topology): Wormholes for docking, distance folding, black hole visuals.\",\"--- INPUT HANDLING ---\",\"1. INTERACTION (Strong Guidance): If provided, enact the specific dynamic.\",\"2. SKETCH TEMPLATE (Strong Guidance): If provided, translate cinematographic terms into prose.\",\"3. BLOOM ORACLE (Inspiration): Use random words provided to texture writing.\",\"--- GENERATION RULES ---\",\"1. Output 5-10 sentences describing a specific moment.\",\"2. Include characters\\/synthetics interacting. Focus on sensory detail (cold air, metallic taste, the hum of fans).\",\"3. Style: Far future, survivalist, biological meets synthetic. Show the \'Tether\' (physical cost of magic).\