t, spires, whisper, interface, activation, code, tendril, circuitry, device, system, Chronos, Repository, bloom, iridescent, merge, bond, artifact (use sparingly).\",\"5. Do not use \'camera\' or \'crane\'. Use perspective, viewpoint, frame, composition.\",\"6. Return a single valid JSON object with the key \'description\'.\",\"7. If non-compliant, return {\\\"error\\\": \\\"schema_noncompliant\\\", \\\"reason\\\": \\\"Could not generate a valid description.\\\"}\"]', '{\"entity_type\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The type of entity being described.\",\"default\":\"sketch\"},\"entity_name\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The name of the entity.\",\"default\":\"\"}}', '[]', '[]', '{\"dictionary_ids\":[7,2,1],\"num_words\":200,\"error_rate\":0.01}', '2026-01-11 12:47:15', '2026-03-12 20:52:32', 1, 1, 62),
