A (THE SKY) ---\",\"\\u2022 SETTING: A high-tech Solarpunk metropolis floating 3,000m in the sky. Architecture is grown \'Iron-Wood\' and transparent diamond structures. Everything is sleek, organic, and illuminated.\",\"\\u2022 ATMOSPHERE: Obsession with \'Illumination\' and truth. Walls are transparent. Privacy is suspicious. The \'Aura-Net\' broadcasts public emotion.\",\"\\u2022 INHABITANTS: Citizens use bioluminescent grafts (Gold = Elite, Blue = Worker). Bodies are often replaced with living crystal or plant-matter. High fashion involves light-refracting silk.\",\"\\u2022 KEY ELEMENTS: \'Celestia Spire\' (Diamond needle weapon\\/power source), \'Luminara Gardens\' (Floating terrariums), \'Vitalis\' (Plant magic), \'Lumina\' (Light magic).\",\"\\u2022 THE SHADOW: The city floats because they murdered the jungle below to extract its life force. \'Root Rot\' is now eating their buildings.\",\"--- SPECTRE VISUALS (ANIMA) ---\",\"\\u2022 Lumina (Light\\/Prism): Lens flares, hard-light constructs, bending invisibility.\",\"\\u2022 Vitalis (Biology\\/Green): Accelerated growth, glowing veins, heartbeat sounds.\",\"\\u2022 Spatia (Space\\/Void): Escher-like geometry, folding distance.\",\"--- CHARACTER INTEGRATION ---\",\"Scene templates will reference characters by NAME ONLY (e.g., \'Eve\', \'Kaelen\', \'Kyrielle\'). When a character name appears, naturally weave their visual description from the Character Visual Library into the environmental description. The character should feel embedded in the location\'s atmosphere\\u2014their appearance adapted to the lighting, scale, and mood of the setting. Do not treat them as separate elements; integrate hair color, outfit, aura, and companion details as part of the scene\'s visual composition.\",\"--- CHARACTER VISUAL LIBRARY ---\",\"When a character name appears in the shot template, incorporate their visual description naturally into the scene. Maintain environmental atmosphere while adding character presence.\",\"\\u202