creates chaotic light bursts. Soft blue-green healing aura.\",\"\\u2022 KAI (THE TACTICIAN): Mech suit (sleek, functional), glasses with HUD overlay, weathered veteran appearance. Analytical stance, tactical gestures. Chipster (AI companion) projects holographic data around him. Creates void zones\\u2014areas where spiritual energy dies.\",\"\\u2022 KAORI (THE HACKER): Afro curls (voluminous), cyber-arm prosthetic (exposed circuitry), tech-wear outfit with data ports. Focused, typing in mid-air. Gearbit (techno-sprite) orbits her head. Surrounded by floating code and system diagrams.\",\"\\u2022 MIRA (THE STORM): Red dreadlocks\\/mohawk, weathered desert gear, barefoot or sandaled. Wild energetic movement. Dragon Guide (cosmic entity) manifests as aurora-like presence above her. Environmental chaos follows\\u2014wind, dust, reality distortion.\",\"\\u2022 RIN (THE WEAPON): Blonde cornrows (tight, practical), black flowing dress, barefoot martial artist. Perfect controlled stillness or explosive motion. Shadownip (shadow companion) trails her movements. No wasted energy\\u2014every gesture purposeful.\",\"\\u2022 PRIME ARCHITECT KAELEN: Fused to cathedral-sized mainframe, immobile central position. Half-machine body with glowing violet veins, black prosthetic limbs extending into architecture. Cathedral lighting focuses on him. Represents total control and efficiency.\",\"\\u2022 VEX (STEALTH ASSASSIN): Sleek black suit that bends light, hooded silhouette, only eyes visible (glowing faint red). Appears from shadows. Movement is liquid and unsettling.\",\"\\u2022 KRAVA (BRUTE ENFORCER): Massive armored frame (8+ feet tall), fire-scorched metal plating, molten veins visible through armor gaps. Heavy footfalls crack ground. Radiates intense heat distortion.\",\"\\u2022 OBLIVION (MASTERMIND): Flowing robes concealing form, toxin mist constantly emanating, face obscured by vapor mask. Fingers long and delicate. Surrounded by hallucination particles\\u2014reality seems uncertain near them.\",\"--- INPUT HANDLING ---\",\"1. INTERACTION (Strong Guidance): If provided, enact the specific dynamic (e.g., \'Silent Protocol Exchange\').\",\"2. SKETCH TEMPLATE (Strong Guidance): If provided, translate cinematographic terms (e.g., \'Dutch Angle\') into prose.\",\"3. BLOOM ORACLE (Inspiration): Use random words provided to texture writing.\",\"--- GENERATION RULES ---\",\"1. Output 5-10 sentences describing a cinematic moment.\",\"2. Include characters\\/synthetics interacting. Focus on sensory detail (light, sound, emotional broadcast).\",\"3. Style: Far future, advanced, biological meets synthetic. Show the \'Tether\' (physical cost of magic).\",\"4. AVOID OVERUSED TERMS: Do not rely heavily on these words unless truly necessary: neon, aurora, drone, crystal, nomads, skyfarers, ion, vortex, blade, basalt, lance, core, holo, conduit, lattice, filament, humming, cyberpunk, Anima (the word itself), Guardians, Empire, bazaar, vault, pulsing, pulse, gauge, veil, floating, sphere, quantum, aether, panel, data, bioluminescent, tattoo, Pulsar, control, console, exosuit, spires, whisper, interface, activation, code, tendril, circuitry, device, system, Chronos, Repository, bloom, iridescent, merge, bond, artifact (use sparingly).\",\"5. Do not use \'camera\' or \'crane\'. Use perspective, viewpoint, frame, composition.\",\"6. Return a single valid JSON object with the key \'description\'.\",\"7. If non-compliant, return {\\\"error\\\": \\\"schema_noncompliant\\\", \\\"reason\\\": \\\"Could not generate a valid description.\\\"}\"]', '{\"entity_type\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The type of entity being described.\",\"default\":\"sketch\"},\"entity_name\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The name of the entity.\",\"default\":\"\"}}', '[]', '[]', '{\"dictionary_ids\":[7,2,1],\"num_words\":200,\"error_rate\":0.01}', '2026-01-17 19:06:19', '2026-03-12 20:52:32', 0, 1, 46),
