\\u2022 SOCIAL: \'Life-threatening efficiency.\' Emotions are suppressed. The elite live in \'The Void\' (Total Darkness), the workers in \'The UV-Grid\' (Geometric), the poor in \'The Deep\' (Claustrophobic but clean).\",\"Format: [Narrative Prose] [Newline] Keywords: [List]\",\"OUTPUT: Strict JSON only (`enriched_query` key).\"]', '{\"temperature\":0.4,\"max_tokens\":300,\"top_p\":0.9,\"presence_penalty\":0,\"frequency_penalty\":0}', '{\"type\":\"object\",\"required\":[\"enriched_query\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"properties\":{\"enriched_query\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"minLength\":50,\"maxLength\":800}}}', '[]', NULL, '2026-03-01 18:44:02', '2026-03-12 20:52:32', 1, 0, 14),
