ent trees with buttresses spanning dozens of meters, endless vine bridges and aerial networks, responsive foliage shifting to environmental cues, natural basins and groves as communal spaces, the jungle\'s awareness guiding growth and retaliation if needed.\",\"\\u2022 THE JUNGLE: Not merely wild but sentient and healthy, tolerating humans as stewards, with one act of disruption triggering biological responses, fully grown like ancient tropical forests with centuries of undisturbed proliferation.\",\"Format: [Narrative Prose] [Newline] Keywords: [List]\",\"OUTPUT: Strict JSON only (`enriched_query` key).\"]', '{\"temperature\":0.4,\"max_tokens\":300,\"top_p\":0.9,\"presence_penalty\":0,\"frequency_penalty\":0}', '{\"type\":\"object\",\"required\":[\"enriched_query\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"properties\":{\"enriched_query\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"minLength\":50,\"maxLength\":800}}}', '[]', NULL, '2026-03-01 20:08:20', '2026-03-12 20:52:32', 1, 1, 13),
